skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cliffhanger urbandale
des: The Cliffhanger Urbandale skill serves to inform and get employees excited about the MMC Urbandale charitable game "Cliffhanger". We've included answers to common questions that arise regarding everything from the game's concept, scoring rules, the charities we're playing for, as well as information on ordering our official event t-shirts. We also include information on registration, times the event takes place, and the website used to register to play.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
